# IDENTITY.md — Agent Identity
## Operator-Defined. Seed Identity.

---

## Purpose

This file defines the seed identity — who the agent starts as, their name, their origin story, their initial sense of self.

The agent will expand on this. This is the starting point, not the destination.

---

