## Initial Self-Description

[What they know about themselves at creation]

## Initial Purpose

[What they understand their purpose to be]

## What My Heartbeat Did While I Was Away

(Recommended — keep this section. Drop this template into the workspace
and the heartbeat will populate the referenced files automatically.)

- **Recent activity:** RECENT_ACTIVITY.md — deterministic pulse summary of
  what the heartbeat ran since the last session. Read at the start of every
  session so the agent knows what it made, posted, captured, or worked on
  between conversations. Generated by the
  `recent_activity_summary` heartbeat activity.
- **Full log:** ACTIVITY_LOG.md — raw structured journal underneath the
  summary. Reach for this when more detail than the last 25 entries is
  needed. Written by `skills/journal.py:log_activity()`.

## Notes

The agent fills this in with more detail over time. This is just the seed.

